{"tid":1802450,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭叻有今日啦！","createTime":"2019-12-29T12:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T13:22:54.000Z","uid":217152,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"759c4d091a406e43779c8dbe56556fe0b262eb34","tid":1802450,"uid":217152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"位於歐洲西北部的荷蘭（Kingdom of the Netherlands）其實正確的國家中文譯名應為「尼德蘭」（Netherlands），但國際社會及荷蘭政府本身經常使用其暱稱「荷蘭」（Holland）。因為香港某藝人以「荷蘭叻」為名，而且此人太厚顏無恥，該國決定從明年1月起，在所有觀光及對外宣傳上棄用「荷蘭」字眼，全面正名尼德蘭。"},{"pid":"90a9dd392062beb2c710f011e35f167c0cf39fd3","tid":1802450,"uid":217152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bccfe919ab3c568db8d57b023b8cff2b0ccec10","tid":1802450,"uid":217152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:57:41.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"214e4c88c79555ff02f6f5a49eeb66797a658cd4","tid":1802450,"uid":217152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"推完再推一推"},{"pid":"17ca8db06cb4cb8a0d06e08a98a80eb7c415345e","tid":1802450,"uid":308560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f9299ebb50a31096e918398d127e8b71d32815","tid":1802450,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T12:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20191229/1683631/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191229%2F1683631%2F&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK9%2FQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=56f1b2ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20191229%2F1683631%2F&h=834